Author: jl777c#5810
Content:
you make some very incorrect assumptions.

i would NEVER support any such attempt to takeover KMD. period. if you doubt this, not sure how i can convince you. maybe the fact that i cannot own any such company shares gives it a financial incentive that you can understand. but it is far more than just the financial aspects. it would break the trust of everybody that has KMD. over the years from NXT assets, SuperNET, BTCD, i have always done my best to make sure the people who supported projects of mine are protected against dilution and certainly against theft.

the place for companies is to build useful services and products using KMD. and already there are such companies that exist, with more to come. each of these are independent and many will have opportunities to invest in them. so there already are companies in the ecosystem.
